      "author": "aidenlx",
      "description": "# Zotero Auto-Update Manifest Host\n\nPermanent release hosting the Mozilla-format update manifests that Zotero polls for auto-update. **Do not delete or rename** — the `update_url` compiled into every shipped XPI resolves to the assets on this release.\n\n| Channel | Manifest | Serves |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| Stable | `update.json` | stable installs |\n| Beta | `update-beta.json` | stable + prerelease installs |\n\nPer-version XPIs live on their own `zt-<version>` releases; this release only carries the update pointers.\n\n- **Add-on:** `zotlit@aidenlx.site`\n- **Compatible Zotero:** 9.0 – 9.*\n- **Last refreshed:** 2026-06-24T10:23:38.975Z for **2.0.0-alpha.1** — updated `update-beta.json`.\n",
      "downloadCount": 0,
      "draft": false,
